name: Click Field Service Edge
description: Add an Field Service Edge Instance to connect your existing Field Service Edge account to the FSA Hub, allowing you to manage your products, customers, tasks, engineers etc. across multiple FSA Elements. You will need your Field Service Edge credentials to add an instance.

configuration.name: Default select fields
